mean_cn: abbr. （=gross domestic product）国内生产总值
mean_en: the abbreviation for 'gross domestic product' (the total value of all the goods and services produced by a country in one year)
sentence: The annual profits from three industries make up the GDP of a country.
sentence_trans: 这三个产业一年中所创造的价值总和即是一个国家的GDP。
